ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：警察一名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有理想咁有志願應該同埋市民一齊上街，而唔係留係警隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講得出呢句姐係你根本認為市民同警察係對立？係唔係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個話上街就係同警察對立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上街都可以合法架喎，只不過有小部分人係違法啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5d8e7f3bd8296f3bda08401ab5e7c843788018","tid":131592,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"又寫啲煽情文搏人同情<br />\n搏人回'警察都有好人'，'不能一竹竿打沉一船人'之類<br />\n*yawn*，有冇第二招？"},{"pid":"fdb30d7307da7412befe21ee23057063f672cde3","tid":131592,"uid":18406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又寫啲煽情文搏人同情<br />\n搏人回'警察都有好人'，'不能一竹竿打沉一船人'之類<br />\n*yawn*，有冇第二招？</blockquote><br />\n係囉<br />\n警察睇到都覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主，真心，你快啲辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d106e5fb0f14889a71924b4c87fe25f84a6688","tid":131592,"uid":20640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:43:03.000Z","msg":"平時保皇狗咁鐘意濫用 政治化 三隻字<br />\n偏偏呢件事完全版政治化就冇人提過<br />\n全部人情緒先導"},{"pid":"bf0ff316f042d2603da6faf62649da7ed8632a86","tid":131592,"uid":33234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主你辭職吧啦，咁有理想咁有志願應該同埋市民一齊上街，而唔係留係警隊。<br />\n更何況樓主呢啲咁高質既人留係警隊都係浪費哂，訓練左6個月，學完啲野好似無入過腦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：警察一名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有理想咁有志願應該同埋市民一齊上街，而唔係留係警隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n